Package: ebergoetzen
Type: Package
Title: Data Management for the Ebergoetzen Terra Network
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Michael Dietze
Maintainer: Michael Dietze <michael.dietze@uni-goettingen.de>
Description: Functions to access, download, parse and organise measurement
    data from the Ebergoetzen Terra Network. The package homogenises 
    workflows from a previous collection of R functions.
